REVISION of the heuristic and genetic system for Genetic AI game
Heuristics totally reworked, now the decision is based on simple factor based score, each score have a maximum of 1 and a minimum of 0, and is multiplied by the corresponding multiplier. Connexity and group counting is now implemented in the heuristics Genetics enhanced, replaced the 4 old 3-bits genes with 13 new 5-bits genes to allow further fine-tuning and enhanced the way genetics options are handled by centralizing the important factors. Seems to converge quite fast (less than 60 generations with 15 peoples)
Documentation update is coming

DOCUMENTATION of the Genetic AI game (plus minor changes)
Changed the depth of bot decision making to 10, centralized the genetic mutation rate and chances, adapted the configuration panels to deal with the new genome length, corrected some docstrings, added some default values to the difficluty settings, and updated some documentation templates to deal with the new connexity module. Also, documentation updated.
No multithreading for this project, I don't know how to implement it cleanly and I don't want to messy up my already quite complex source code. Some stats visualization and some genobase file formatting enhancement might be useful.
